org.cdnomlqko.jglutil.examples

Class SceneExample

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cdnomlqko.jglutil.examples.ApplicationBase
      • org.cdnomlqko.jglutil.examples.SceneExample

  • public class SceneExample
extends ApplicationBase
    A test. Implements a sample scene with 2 stanford dragons: one red and one yellow, one yellow cube, one unchanging light and another that changes color. Controll camera with WASD, Shift and Space. '1' toggles input and visibility of the mouse.
    Author:
    CDnoMlqko
